      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众云童引众仙同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001003_e00002",
      "play_id": "02001003",
      "scene_id": "02001003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同粉蝶儿",
      "speakers": [
        "众仙"
      ],
      "text": "海岛逍遥，采仙药，长生不老，稳坐着碧云车，好趋扶摇。过沧溟，排阊阖，一霎里飞腾光耀，不虚那桂酒佳肴。献寿筵擎来奇宾，擎来奇宾。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001003_e00003",
      "play_id": "02001003",
      "scene_id": "02001003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "众仙"
      ],
      "text": "碧瓦朱楹十二楼，瞳眬日窟尽仙州。方知前路无多远，白鹤长添海屋筹。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
